channel.title: Hosters?
channel.description:
Hey, I'm Dylza, I have a Wonderful Server Called "New Fr33sc4p3" It is great, But...The Problem is...I can't host it on my computer, or my dads, My comp is too slow, And My dads connection is getting taken off and he aint letting me no more. So I need a new Hoster that could host my server, And if you Are up for it and I say you can be, Then you can be "Co-Owner" of the server, Although, You must have MSN Messenger and know how to Host a server, I don't EXPECT No-ip. But I would Love it, I can also have ham though.
Thanks,
[shadow=red,left]Dylza[/shadow]
